rows.label: bf08310100_0002
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*gasp*

rows.label: bf08310100_0004
rows.name: The Great Void is almost gone.

rows.label: bf08310100_0006
rows.name: That makes sense, since Serpent was what created the Great Void.

rows.label: bf08310100_0008
rows.name: I see.

rows.label: bf08310100_0010
rows.name:
So with Serpent gone,
the Great Void vanished as well.

rows.label: bf08310100_0012
rows.name:
If we were above the Cloud Sea,
we could have just gone straight across.

rows.label: bf08310100_0014
rows.name: It doesn't seem impossible to climb, but...

rows.label: bf08310100_0020
rows.name: This is nothing like a casual hiking trip.

rows.label: bf08310100_0030
rows.name: Everyone, over here.

rows.label: bf08310100_0040
rows.name: Homura?

rows.label: bf08310100_0050
rows.name:
The insides of the World Tree... I'd never have
thought...

rows.label: bf08310100_0060
rows.name:
It seems like giant plants are wrapped around
an artificial tower.

rows.label: bf08310100_0070
rows.name: We should be able to use this to go upward.

rows.label: bf08310100_0080
rows.name:
Up...? Wait, Homura,
what did you just do?

rows.label: bf08310100_0090
rows.name: I'm not entirely sure myself.

rows.label: bf08310100_0100
rows.name: My body is remembering something on its own.

rows.label: bf08310100_0110
rows.name:
This must be another power that [System:Ruby rt=Father ]God[/System:Ruby]
bestowed upon the Master Blade.

rows.label: bf08310100_0120
rows.name: That's precisely why we need to hurry.

rows.label: bf08310100_0130
rows.name: Homura...

rows.label: bf08310100_0140
rows.name:
This knowledge is instinctual for me.
Metsu must have the same abilities.

rows.label: bf08310100_0150
rows.name: Metsu too...

rows.label: bf08310100_0160
rows.name: Looks like some type of elevator.

rows.label: bf08310100_0170
rows.name: I-it's all glass?

rows.label: bf08310100_0180
rows.name:
Prince, you hate high places, don't you?
Keep your eyes closed.

rows.label: bf08310100_0190
rows.name: Let's go.
